---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms of use for Wind Turbine Jobs."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 py-14 pb-20 sm:px-6">
    <div class="prose-content">
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="lead">By using this site you agree to these terms.</p>

      <h2>About this service</h2>
      <p>
        Wind Turbine Jobs is an aggregation service. We collect publicly available job postings from
        employer career pages and display them here. We are not the employer, recruiter, or hiring
        party for any listed position.
      </p>

      <h2>Job listings</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Listings are sourced automatically and may be out of date by the time you view them.</li>
        <li>We make no warranty as to the accuracy, completeness, or availability of any listing.</li>
        <li>
          All "Apply" links go to the employer's own career page. We have no control over the
          employer's hiring process, timeline, or decisions.
        </li>
        <li>
          We are not responsible for any content on external employer sites.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
      <p>You agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Scrape or systematically download listing data for commercial purposes</li>
        <li>Use automated tools to submit spam or abuse the subscribe form</li>
        <li>Attempt to circumvent Cloudflare Turnstile or other bot-protection mechanisms</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        Job titles, descriptions, and employer names remain the property of their respective
        employers. We aggregate and display this information as factual data about available
        employment, which is permissible under copyright law.
      </p>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        This site is provided "as is" without any warranty. We are not liable for any loss or
        damage arising from your use of this site or from applying to jobs listed here.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance
        of the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any questions, email <a href="mailto:legal@windturbinejobs.com">legal@windturbinejobs.com</a>.
      </p>

      <p class="updated">Last updated: May 2025</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-content {
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
  }
  .prose-content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--foreground);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }
  .prose-content .lead {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .prose-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--foreground);
    margin: 2.25rem 0 0.625rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }
  .prose-content p,
  .prose-content li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }
  .prose-content ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }
  .prose-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .prose-content a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .prose-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .prose-content .updated {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
</style>
